project:
Ah, the splendid game of "Where's Wally?" Ah, those were the golden days of childhood, a treasure trove of joy! Now, dear friend, we propose to put your finely-honed detection skills to the ultimate test amidst a cacophony of distractions. Should you emerge victorious, a Christmas gift of enigmatic riddles shall be bestowed upon thee, revealing the true extent of your sleuthing prowess.

Picture this: a myriad of diversions, a bustling spectacle of misdirection akin to a whimsical carnival. Yet, in this merry pandemonium, a suspect lurks incognito. It is your charge, nay, your honor, to pinpoint this elusive miscreant amidst the revelry.

Triumph, and the gift of Christmas riddles shall be yours! Fail not, for the anticipation of unraveling mysteries awaits, promising mirth and mental acrobatics. Go forth, valiant seeker, and may your eyes be as keen as an owl's in a field of mice. The stage is set, the distractions aplenty â€“ let the festive challenge commence!

Pick one and enjoy the game :)
Super easy
Easy
Medium
Hard
Challenge
Wally, our protagonist! You always need to find him.

Did you know Wally's group? They are Wilma, Wally's long time friend. Odlaw, our antagonist! His dream is to be so cool as Wally. And Wizard Whitebeard, a powerful mage who sometimes send Wally to some cool adventures.
Meet woof! Wally's dog. The big problem is that you only can find his tail. It's such a challenge, uh?
Wally has a fan-club! They're called The Wally Watchers and they often appear during our protagonist's adventure. Look for them if you can :D
The ultimate challenge! This one is only for the bravest. Find the five items listed in the image. Be brave!
Time to play! First, select the difficulty level :D

Ah, splendid detective extraordinaire! Bravo on your triumphant discovery of the elusive Wally, proving your mettle in the noble art of hide-and-seek. But hark! The grandiosity of your accomplishment pales in comparison to the challenge that lies ahead.

Prepare thyself, for a clandestine art thief has dared to abscond with a masterpiece crafted by none other than the illustrious Paul Klee. Fear not, for an epistle of enigma shall soon grace your presence. Within its cryptic verses lies the key to unraveling the whereabouts of this rogue purveyor of pilfered paintings.

Fret not, dear sleuth, for even the mighty Google may lend its digital wisdom to aid you in this perilous quest. Yet, be warned, for relying too heavily on such electronic crutches may brand thee as a seeker of shortcuts in the eyes of the connoisseurs of cunning.

Embark upon this whimsical journey, unraveling riddles with the finesse of a feline in pursuit of a particularly elusive ball of yarn. Each successful deciphering shall beckon forth another missive, leading you ever closer to unmasking the artful art thief.

Let the mirthful mystery unfold, and may your wits be as sharp as a well-honed quill pen in the hands of a mischievous muse!
